title: # 375 - Ethan Page & ME
description:
Hey Guys! Today I sit down with Impact Wrestling champ Ethan Page! We talk about how he became a professional wrestler, how much we love The Rock, an average work week for a pro wrestler, and we pitch a movie idea to a producer over the phone!

Check out Ethans Youtube Vlog here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOSPD57dInYd9Id3bHqZsWg

Text me! 323-208-0844
